title: Mahou Shoujo Lyrical Nanoha A's Portable: The Gears of Destiny - Material Musume.
original_name: 魔法少女リリカルなのは A's PORTABLE -THE GEARS OF DESTINY- マテリアル娘。
sinopse:
Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha A's Portable: The Gears of Destiny - Material Girls. is the 4-koma comedy manga, with the Materials being the main characters.

(Source: nanoha.wikia)
